    "body": "**<sub><sub>![P2 Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/P2-yellow?style=flat)</sub></sub>  Stop locking 2.9.14 to non-runtime metadata**\n\nFor the 2.9.14 release path, this updated version assertion still sits in `test_pyproject_declares_non_runtime_tooling_baseline`, which continues to require `runtime_behavior_changed = false` in `pyproject.toml`. This commit's release metadata and notes explicitly mark 2.9.14 as runtime-changing (new playback presets/default hold-mode behavior), so the test now protects stale tooling metadata and lets release/readiness consumers classify a runtime-changing package as a no-runtime cleanup.\n\nUseful? React with 👍 / 👎.",
